{"id":"a9af6af8c20e029b1f1fe1c7f252b94ea38771d4cf58ebda2a23b1e9a22ce479","item_id":"de7bcb979f:0","text":"RenderMan for Blender 会持续获得更新和错误修复，因此请参考 RenderMan for Blender GitHub 页面获取最新的每夜构建版本。"}
{"id":"348249d696fd661abd4bc76833b814789be8c1b878cf1d14a408fbecb977c347","item_id":"de7bcb979f:1","text":"请注意，GitHub 页面上的 releases（发布包）并不总是经过完整测试的版本，因此请自行承担使用风险。"}
{"id":"50e1dd3a7a9c8a0a1fb195fe37ebcf06ca8adfe8e49d2349e0a1a26a6917cc93","item_id":"de7bcb979f:2","text":"GitHub 页面位于："}
{"id":"f6d4b0bccbd170295ff4e970dbeaf5024fade3d107fd29d830dff0122f5e50cb","item_id":"de7bcb979f:3","text":"https://github.com/prman-pixar/RenderManForBlender"}
{"id":"13ad59c4428fce69e6c1eecd06d3c59e6cba9ffe5a2b6692bfe6b597b3d006b3","item_id":"de7bcb979f:4","text":"安装时，请使用安装 RenderMan for Blender 的常规方法。"}
{"id":"c587bf911a73348c681f26301a9eb2c245ebb2c5f9dd78d61d4a3128f0b01871","item_id":"de7bcb979f:5","text":"下载 RenderManforBlender.zip 文件"}
{"id":"0d606fada6e53c147ffebd25922165d91706c3242e72e6eb69373df22c8982d0","item_id":"de7bcb979f:6","text":"Start（启动）Blender，并从"}
{"id":"3a2e9e3786b380de311020bc25f51d774e7c0fc129275fd5b56b7be052cc07fc","item_id":"de7bcb979f:7","text":"File → User Preferences → Add-ons"}
{"id":"7fb1485dcb85f059349c53201f16d03eb9f8be16fb22b95d16ac586f6316e37b","item_id":"de7bcb979f:8","text":"安装已下载的 .zip 文件。"}
{"id":"05a36fd95b9151ce2369189af7c264502d814562926571e2275040488eb8316f","item_id":"de7bcb979f:9","text":"将渲染器切换为 RenderMan，然后开始使用。"}
